data.description: Nestled on  tranquil cul-de-sac, this superb split-entry home offers a spacious and inviting ambiance with 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. The open living and dining areas feature soaring vaulted ceilings, bathing the space in natural light. The kitchen, complete with a central island, serves as the heart of the home for family gatherings. A generously sized primary bedroom includes a 3/4 bath, while three total upper-level bedrooms provide ample space. The lower level unveils an expansive family room with a cozy fireplace, complemented by a gracious entry foyer. Recent updates, including LVP flooring, fresh paint, and new trim, along with a roof and siding replacement within the past three years, offer peace of mind and curb appeal. The unfinished lower level presents options to create a fifth bedroom, a workshop, or a home gym. With endless possibilities, this home beckons as a versatile and comfortable place to call home.
